E/Roman/Texts/Suetonius/de_Grammaticis*.html#ref7
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">7</A>
"Men of letters," from <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">littera</SPAN>, while <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">grammaticus</SPAN> is from the corresponding Greek word <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">γράμμα</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


