"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">17</A>
The word is evidently corrupt; perhaps we should read Perialges (<SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">περιαλγής</SPAN>), "The <SPAN CLASS="whole">Sorrow</SPAN>&shy;ful Man." Turnebus


<A ID="p409x"></A>suggested <SPAN LANG="el" CLASS="Greek">περὶ ἀλογίας</SPAN>, a treatise on the folly of teachers in submitting to such unjust treatment.


